OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA fine, largely settled day
OL,6,Fwith plenty of sunshine. A few early
OL,7,Fshowers will quickly clear southwards,
OL,8,Fleaving dry conditions. Feeling cool
OL,9,Fin brisk northerly winds, particularly
OL,10,Falong coastal areas.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FClear overnight skies will
OL,13,Fallow temperatures to fall away
OL,14,Fquickly, with a rural frost forming.
OL,15,FCloud will increase from the north
OL,16,Fearly on, introducing some light rain.
OL,17,FWinds falling light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
