OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FA band of cloud and patchy
OL,6,Flight rain will clear south during the
OL,7,Fmorning. Blustery, scattered showers
OL,8,Fwill follow with sunny intervals.
OL,9,FWinds strengthening through the day.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,12,FFrequent blustery showers on Wednesday
OL,13,Fand Thursday, occasionally heavy with
OL,14,Fa risk of thunder. Friday dry and
OL,15,Fmostly cloudy, with some bright or
OL,16,Fsunny spells. Feeling rather cool.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
